title: NZ loses appeal against Olympic football ejection
text: NZ loses appeal against Olympic football ejection Friday, 23 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) WELLINGTON, New Zealand (AP) The Oceania Football Confederation has rejected New Zealand's appeal against disqualification from the region's Olympic qualifying tournament for using an ineligible player.
